Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝カード提出直前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:56.28,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji hesitated just before\Ndealing the Emperor card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは思わず躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悩んだ末 市民カードを提出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.30,default,,0,0,0,,After some consideration,\Nhe played the Citizen card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸運にも勝利を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.17,default,,0,0,0,,That resulted in a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが発端となってカイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川のイカサマに気づく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.17,default,,0,0,0,,That was when Kaiji noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:07.52,default,,0,0,0,,...that Tonegawa was cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:09.85,default,,0,0,0,,The device in Kaiji's ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの耳の装置と利根川の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕時計に仕組まれたトリックに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.68,default,,0,0,0,,...and Tonegawa's wristwatch,\Nwere linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ひらめく　利根川殺し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.31,default,,0,0,0,,And then it struck him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:20.66,default,,0,0,0,,A devilish plan to kill the demon,\Nto kill Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔を殺す悪魔的奇手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.19,default,,0,0,0,,While taking a break,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,休憩を取ったカイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突如 異常な行動に出る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:26.00,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji does something unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:32.46,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Fierce God
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん　どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でこんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:35.67,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:39.17,default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:42.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やらなきゃよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:41.38,default,,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.47,default,,0,0,0,,I have to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしなきゃなんねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:47.89,default,,0,0,0,,...in order to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つためには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてください　カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.49,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Please stop, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに気がついたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.68,default,,0,0,0,,So, he finally realised it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ　そのとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.01,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その装置は単に鼓膜を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破るためだけの機械ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:18.80,default,,0,0,0,,That device isn't simply a tool\Nto destroy your eardrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の脈拍 体温 血圧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発汗を感知し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:23.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's a device that monitors\Nyour pulse, body temperature,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.51,default,,0,0,0,,blood pressure and perspiration,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時計に送信する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感知器 送信機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.26,default,,0,0,0,,which are transmitted\Nto the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.59,default,,0,0,0,,Even now,\Nit's sending data here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も律儀に送ってくれるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:37.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレで起こっている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:37.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の心中の変化をな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:37.26,default,,0,0,0,,about your emotional changes\Nwhile you're in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.96,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Body Temperature, Perspiration]\N [Blood Pressure, Pulse]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暴れてる 暴れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.26,default,,0,0,0,,He's lost it, he's lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姿は見えずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで手に取るようではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:46.49,default,,0,0,0,,Although I can't see you,\NI feel like I'm there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,装置を外すことは不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.78,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible\Nto take off the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れぬように留め金が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり耳にかみついている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.75,default,,0,0,0,,It's clamped tightly onto your\Nears to prevent removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:03:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強引に外そうとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:03:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このﾘﾓｺﾝが感知し 知らせてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.60,default,,0,0,0,,If you try\Nremoving it by force,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.09,default,,0,0,0,,this remote control\Nwill detect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は暴れることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべての数値をマックスにし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.22,default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to\Nwreck the device...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役に立たない状態に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しようとしているのだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.99,default,,0,0,0,,...by acting violently\Nto max out the readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょせん そんなものは浅知恵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.36,default,,0,0,0,,That's just shallow thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの勝ちは動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:15.12,default,,0,0,0,,My victory remains assured,\Nno matter how you resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう あらがおうともな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:24.28,default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! What do you\Nget out of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてください　何になるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことをして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん 変ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.14,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you're behaving strangely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変でいい　変でなきゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.15,default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.17,default,,0,0,0,,I have to be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逸脱してなきゃ悪魔を殺せない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.35,default,,0,0,0,,I can't defeat that demon\Nby normal means!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川を倒せない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.14,default,,0,0,0,,I can't defeat Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常軌を逸してこそ開かれる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.56,default,,0,0,0,,By throwing away\Ncommon sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちへの道が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.56,default,,0,0,0,,It's the path to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.90,default,,0,0,0,,Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.67,default,,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:19.93,default,,0,0,0,,18!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.43,default,,0,0,0,,My wager for this round\Nis 18 mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の張りは18ミリで勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:31.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:31.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倒す　お前だけはな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.44,default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat you!\NI'll surely defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.40,default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふ… 実にすばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.18,default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めての体験だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.28,default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time\Nexperiencing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うまでもなく勝ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:47.19,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa, I'm sure you know\Nthat you have to win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.43,default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I've seen many types\Nof death up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは実にいろいろな死にざまを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳から針を差し込み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.17,default,,0,0,0,,But piercing of the eardrum\Nwith a needle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その針で鼓膜から脳を破り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.27,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the first time\NI'm seeing death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでもらう死に方は初めてじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.44,default,,0,0,0,,...by piercing of the brain\Nthrough the eardrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 想像もつかん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.58,default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI can't imagine how it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう のたうつか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.30,default,,0,0,0,,How will you writhe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しみは一瞬か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.18,default,,0,0,0,,Will the suffering\Nbe for an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:15.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも長時間に及ぶのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:14.68,default,,0,0,0,,Or will it be\Nprolonged over time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.19,default,,0,0,0,,Will you throw up and\Nlose control over your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嘔吐か　失禁か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けいれんか　発狂か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.94,default,,0,0,0,,Will you have a fit?\NOr will you go mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.40,default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:37.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカード　カイジ　決死の11戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.21,default,,0,0,0,,It's the 11th round of E-Card\Nand Kaiji is desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.94,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[Slave]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張りは装置のリミットいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.36,default,,0,0,0,,It's the furthest that the\Ndevice's needle can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼓膜のはるか先まで貫く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.45,default,,0,0,0,,A distance that will pierce\Nfar beyond the eardrum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.95,default,,0,0,0,,18 mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いがカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:54.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この回でお前は死ぬことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.23,default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:56.46,default,,0,0,0,,But you'll die in this round,\Nwrithing in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のたうちながらな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目　提出は利根川から
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.46,default,,0,0,0,,The first card will be\Ndealt by Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:06.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血圧が作動していない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.56,default,,0,0,0,,His blood pressure isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.51,default,,0,0,0,,A malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故障したか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが　相当派手にぶつけたな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.86,default,,0,0,0,,That idiot must have\Nhit it quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ほかの計器は正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.85,default,,0,0,0,,However, the other\Ninstruments are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.60,default,,0,0,0,,So, long as I know\Nyour heartbeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:21.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈拍 体温 発汗が分かれば十分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.68,default,,0,0,0,,body temperature and\Nperspiration, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら暴れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.91,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how wild you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.37,default,,0,0,0,,your pulse, body temperature\Nand perspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈や体温や発汗の乱れは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでも続かぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.69,default,,0,0,0,,...cannot remain\Nat a high forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,収まらざるを得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間と共にな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:32.09,default,,0,0,0,,It has to calm down over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば ただ待てばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.42,default,,0,0,0,,It looks like\NI'll just have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.16,default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nyour body returns to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の体が収まるのをな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただゆっくりと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.79,default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.53,default,,0,0,0,,Three minutes pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３分経過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.54,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NWhy are you wasting time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？何 ぐずぐずしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:07:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理を言うな　18ミリの大勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:07:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慎重にもなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:58.00,default,,0,0,0,,Don't be unreasonable.\N18 mm is a big bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.78,default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:14.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分後 利根川 ようやく提出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.30,default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.80,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa finally makes his move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けてカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.82,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji responds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.12,default,,0,0,0,,And they open the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてオープン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民と市民　引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.81,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen versus Citizen.\NA draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの反応を見れば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を出したかが分かる利根川が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:35.63,default,,0,0,0,,From Kaiji's reaction, Tonegawa\Nknew which card he would play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目に勝負カードを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出すわけもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.47,default,,0,0,0,,Hence, he chose not to deal\Nhis trump as the first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またカイジもそのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重々知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.98,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji is fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.03,default,,0,0,0,,The problem is the second card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:47.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は２枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:47.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先出しは奴隷側のカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.03,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji starts by playing\Nthe Slave card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.77,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けて利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び長考
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.05,default,,0,0,0,,Once again, he takes his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下がってきた　はげてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツのメッキが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.66,default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.28,default,,0,0,0,,His pretence is wearing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽りの興奮が引き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.02,default,,0,0,0,,The false excitement\Nis fading,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,浮かび上がるヤツのおびえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.78,default,,0,0,0,,and his fears are rising up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.22,default,,0,0,0,,His raw emotions, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈も体温も発汗も やや高いが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.76,default,,0,0,0,,His pulse, body temperature\Nand perspiration levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.53,default,,0,0,0,,...are a little high,\Nbut it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうほぼ正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見かけほど興奮していない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.45,default,,0,0,0,,He's not as agitated\Nas he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:27.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということはヤツのカードは市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:26.58,default,,0,0,0,,Which means that\Nhis card is a Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負カードの奴隷を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出しているなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.09,default,,0,0,0,,If he's playing his trump,\Nthe Slave card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し興奮していい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.97,default,,0,0,0,,one could expect\Na bigger reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し高い数値を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時計が示していい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.66,default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for the watch to\Nshow me higher figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体が反応していていい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.48,default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for your body to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなくヤツのカードは市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.48,default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake that\Nhis card is a Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が 一応 念を押すか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.69,default,,0,0,0,,But I'll have\Nto be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は市民で行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.70,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with a Citizen next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.26,default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kaiji?\NJust to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ カイジ君　無難にな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応なしか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈 体温 発汗に変化なし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.25,default,,0,0,0,,No reaction,\Nno change in his pulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.28,default,,0,0,0,,body temperature\Nor perspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,困ったような気配を見せているが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれはブラフ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.00,default,,0,0,0,,You're showing me\Nthat you're troubled,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.35,default,,0,0,0,,but that's just a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしを欺く演技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.35,default,,0,0,0,,An act to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈や体温に変化がない以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.45,default,,0,0,0,,So long as his pulse and\Nbody temperature do not change,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつはこの市民を恐れていない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.09,default,,0,0,0,,he's not afraid\Nof this Citizen card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり ヤツのカードは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,市民に殺される奴隷ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:25.32,default,,0,0,0,,Thus, his card is not the Slave,\Nwhich the Citizen would kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし奴隷なら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな稚拙な誘導にも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:29.21,default,,0,0,0,,If it were a Slave,\Nhis body would surely react,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず体は反応する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.32,default,,0,0,0,,despite this childish bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応してはまずいと思っても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応してしまうのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:35.80,default,,0,0,0,,He'd react despite knowing\Nthat it's to his disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:40.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが人間の体　生理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.81,default,,0,0,0,,That's how a human body is.\NIt's instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば こっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.81,default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.81,default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.05,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 君は死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.15,default,,0,0,0,,Now, you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.80,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa plays the Emperor card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.72,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.04,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.08,default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:32.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふ… さあ 開けたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:32.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せめてもの慈悲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.32,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.82,default,,0,0,0,,I'll be merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開けた瞬間に殺してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.81,default,,0,0,0,,The moment you show your card,\NI'll end your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.34,default,,0,0,0,,This way, you won't suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しまぬようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:56.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開けられぬか 自分からは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:55.10,default,,0,0,0,,You can't open it\Non your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.97,default,,0,0,0,,That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:59.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理もない　ならば…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.38,default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってたよな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.95,default,,0,0,0,,You said so, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷は持たざる者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,猶予のない虐げられし者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.01,default,,0,0,0,,The Slave has nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.78,default,,0,0,0,,An oppressed figure\Nwith nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし その何も持たない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしようもない奴隷だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:18.10,default,,0,0,0,,But because he has nothing\Nand can do nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王を討つと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.20,default,,0,0,0,,the Slave\Ncan kill the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.44,default,,0,0,0,,And what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが俺と仲間のギリギリ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.94,default,,0,0,0,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:29.68,default,,0,0,0,,...the very last words of\Nmy comrades and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の淵での最後の意地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.41,default,,0,0,0,,The last of our pride\Nfrom the realm of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:35.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け取れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.12,default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.39,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.26,default,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.42,default,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　勝った！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんの勝ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.04,default,,0,0,0,,- He won! \N- He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:18.89,default,,0,0,0,,- He did it! \N- Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな　なぜだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.90,default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.90,default,,0,0,0,,Why? How did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大量出血で身体反応そのものが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱まったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.88,default,,0,0,0,,Have his bodily responses\Nweakened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.82,default,,0,0,0,,...due to\Nmassive blood loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 仮にそうだとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:43.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何らかの反応があるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.98,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:42.72,default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there should\Nat least be a slight response.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:46.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは故障か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.96,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nit malfunctioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血圧以外の計器にも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何らかの誤作動が？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.72,default,,0,0,0,,Did the other\Ninstruments malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう考えるしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.42,default,,0,0,0,,Most likely,\Nthat's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ま… まさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:02.47,default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.84,default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　今頃 気がついたか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅すぎるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.44,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NDid you only just realise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.18,default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ろうかい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボケた老獪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.91,default,,0,0,0,,You cunning old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マヌケな人殺しめ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.12,default,,0,0,0,,You foolish murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.16,default,,0,0,0,,The toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレに人がいるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引っ立ててこい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.66,default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in the toilet!\NBring him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.26,default,,0,0,0,,You scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,み… 耳が…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:47.17,default,,0,0,0,,His ear... His ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:49.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳が… 耳がない！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.28,default,,0,0,0,,His ear is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川先生　いました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.49,default,,0,0,0,,Mr Tonegawa, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… こいつの手に装置と
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,み… 耳が…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.52,default,,0,0,0,,The device is in his hands.\NTogether with an ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう まさに利根川が追っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脈 発汗 体温は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.27,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.13,default,,0,0,0,,The pulse, perspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.20,default,,0,0,0,,...and body temperature\Nthat Tonegawa monitored...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジのものではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男のものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.31,default,,0,0,0,,...were not Kaiji's,\Nbut this man's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは耳ごと装置を取り外し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.22,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji removed the device\Ntogether with his ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男に持たせることによって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.31,default,,0,0,0,,...and by making the man\Nhold on to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽りの情報を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川に送っていたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.05,default,,0,0,0,,sent false information\Nto Tonegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸いだったのは この装置が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:37.48,default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the device\Nis not limited to the ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生体に触れてさえいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応する方式であったことである
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.06,default,,0,0,0,,It will react, as long as in\Ncontact with a living part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血圧だけは別の方式で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感知していたので
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.14,default,,0,0,0,,As blood pressure was measured\Nusing other methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳を取り外した瞬間に消えたが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.60,default,,0,0,0,,it disappeared the moment\Nthe ear was removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は気づかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.26,default,,0,0,0,,But it escaped Tonegawa's notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう意味では おごる利根川の
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミスにも支えられた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.84,default,,0,0,0,,In that sense,\Nit was a wild strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,荒い戦略だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.64,default,,0,0,0,,...backed up by\NTonegawa's arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.78,default,,0,0,0,,In any case, Kaiji managed\Nto secure a victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:00.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ともかくカイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:00.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もぎ取ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,筆舌に尽くしがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛みと恐れを乗り越え
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.86,default,,0,0,0,,A victory beyond description,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.73,default,,0,0,0,,that overcame pain and fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔から１勝を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.52,default,,0,0,0,,18 mm multiplied\Nby 5 is 90!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,18ミリかける５で90
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは900万を獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:16.83,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji won 9 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大金　カイジからすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:22.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目もくらむような大金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:22.52,default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge amount that\Nis blinding to Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまでの勝ち分210万を加え
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.51,default,,0,0,0,,Adding in the 2.1 million\Nthat he won earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.97,default,,0,0,0,,it's a total of 11.1 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,計 1110万
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.58,default,,0,0,0,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまらん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったくクソ面白くもない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.58,default,,0,0,0,,This is not fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使えぬ男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.59,default,,0,0,0,,What a useless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つくづく愛想が尽きた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.51,default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.09,default,,0,0,0,,You're completely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく新しい死に方が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見られそうだったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:49.32,default,,0,0,0,,I waited so long expecting\Nto see a new method of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のくだらないミスで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その機を逃した
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:53.10,default,,0,0,0,,It slipped away because of\Nyour stupid mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:58.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら わしはお前を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:58.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買いかぶっていたようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:58.23,default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I esteemed you\Ntoo highly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなザマでは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今あるポストからの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:03.33,default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have to consider demoting\Nyou from your current post.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降格も考えねばならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.61,default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:09.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大詰めで弱い人間は信用できぬわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.61,default,,0,0,0,,Humans who are weak towards\Nthe end can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりそれは 管理はできても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負のできぬ男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.08,default,,0,0,0,,This proves that\Nyou're only good at...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.45,default,,0,0,0,,...management but\Nnot at competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平常時の仕事は無難にこなしても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:18.11,default,,0,0,0,,A man with difficulty when\Nthings proceed normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緊急時には
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソの役にも立たぬということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.63,default,,0,0,0,,but who is useless\Nin times of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンチはしのげず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャンスは逃す
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:24.36,default,,0,0,0,,You can't survive crises and\Nallow chances to slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とても人の上に立つ器ではないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.23,default,,0,0,0,,You're certainly not the type\Nwho can rise above others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　はげたな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の化けの皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.00,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa, you have\Nshown your true colours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二流だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょせん お前は指示待ち人間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.32,default,,0,0,0,,You're second-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.11,default,,0,0,0,,You're the kind of person who\Nonly waits for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声こそ荒立てぬものの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.04,default,,0,0,0,,Though his voice remains calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急所を突く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ネチネチとした会長の罵倒が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:45.22,default,,0,0,0,,the director continues his verbal\Nabuse directed at sore spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな中 急速にこの場の空気が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弛緩していく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:49.53,default,,0,0,0,,Throughout this,\Nthe tension quickly eases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:53.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji didn't reach his\Ntarget of 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万という
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当初の目標には届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし耳の装置を外したトリックを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,12戦目も使えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:56.99,default,,0,0,0,,If he could have\Napplied the same trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.08,default,,0,0,0,,...of removing the device\Nin the 12th round,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万という線もあり得たが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.73,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji could have\Nreached 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがついえた今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11戦目が事実上 カイジの終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.65,default,,0,0,0,,But now that it's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.66,default,,0,0,0,,the 11th round was\NKaiji's last decisive battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に12戦目があったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.88,default,,0,0,0,,For example, even if a\N12th round was held,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ミリか２ミリ張って終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.26,default,,0,0,0,,the most he could wager\Nwas 1 or 2 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.98,default,,0,0,0,,It would be a match\Nof that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただそれだけの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:18.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな弛緩した空気が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:18.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの激痛感を覚醒させる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:19.14,default,,0,0,0,,The relaxed atmosphere\Nrevives Kaiji's sense of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,B-Bring me a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タ… タオルを…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.81,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この血痕が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:40.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いもかけずカイジに与える
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:39.57,default,,0,0,0,,However, this bloodstain\Ninadvertently strikes Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:44.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるひらめき 戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:43.56,default,,0,0,0,,A flash of insight!\NAnother strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… 待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.38,default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.08,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:01.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつの人間性 観察力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.19,default,,0,0,0,,The nature of this man,\Nhis powers of observation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに この出血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.79,default,,0,0,0,,...and this bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまく使えば勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.43,default,,0,0,0,,If I use this well,\NI can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる　12戦も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.54,default,,0,0,0,,I can win the 12th round too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし100パーセントじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:12.43,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not 100% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思惑どおり利根川が こっちの罠に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はまってくれればいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.80,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine if Tonegawa falls\Nfor my trap as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし空回りして策が滑ったら死…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.78,default,,0,0,0,,But if the plan fails,\Nit'll be death for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:24.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'll die.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな危険を冒さなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:26.41,default,,0,0,0,,Even without taking such a risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 これだけの金が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.28,default,,0,0,0,,I've already gained\Nthis much in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうカイジが考えた刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.92,default,,0,0,0,,The very moment Kaiji\Nthought about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直感する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雷光に打たれたかのように
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.42,default,,0,0,0,,he had a gut feeling,\Nas if he was struck by lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1110万止まり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.66,default,,0,0,0,,At the moment,\Nhe has 11.1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ道をつかみながら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆してそれを手放すようでは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:44.89,default,,0,0,0,,Despite being on\Nthe path to victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに今 得ているこの1110万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.33,default,,0,0,0,,if he shrinks back in fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.33,default,,0,0,0,,the 11.1 million he'd amassed\Nwould be his limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これがリミット
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分には生涯 これ以上の金は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかめないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.90,default,,0,0,0,,He felt that he'd never be\Nable to gain a larger amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,という予感 直感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.44,default,,0,0,0,,...for the rest of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.48,default,,0,0,0,,A gut feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:19:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はチャンスを自ら閉じてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:01.48,default,,0,0,0,,I'm closing the door\Nto this chance myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の限界はここ… ここ止まりと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.22,default,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの誰でもない俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺自身が見限ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.72,default,,0,0,0,,It's not anyone else\Nbut myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.93,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の その可能性を区切ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:18.23,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's separating\Nwhat I can or cannot do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できることと できないことに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.92,default,,0,0,0,,No!\NWhat am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！何をしてる 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,区切るなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.34,default,,0,0,0,,Don't cut yourself off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだみんなのためにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前だ　もっと前に行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of\Nthose who died too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.01,default,,0,0,0,,I have to move forward!\NI have to overcome it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.71,default,,0,0,0,,My fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:37.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,越えろ　恐れを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.12,default,,0,0,0,,My hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:40.88,default,,0,0,0,,My suspicions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,躊躇を 疑心を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.32,default,,0,0,0,,Push them aside and move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押しのけていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸い敵は今 心を緩めている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャンスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.96,default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the enemy's\Nmind is distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.56,default,,0,0,0,,It's an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ行け　もう一度 こぎ出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.42,default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:56.30,default,,0,0,0,,Set sail once more into\Nthe great sea of challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負の大海へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:59.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つんだ　もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.72,default,,0,0,0,,To win another victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためには これか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.81,default,,0,0,0,,In order to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.76,default,,0,0,0,,I must start with\Nthese three cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず この３枚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:18.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひざへ　そして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.55,default,,0,0,0,,He places them on his lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:20.56,default,,0,0,0,,And puts one into his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚を手中に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川をうかがう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.56,default,,0,0,0,,He glances at Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:29.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に11戦目で使った２枚を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:29.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏返す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:27.38,default,,0,0,0,,Next, he takes two cards\Nfrom the 11th round...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.51,default,,0,0,0,,...and flips them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに手中のカードを落とし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.76,default,,0,0,0,,He then puts down the card\Nthat was in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ　いまいましい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.78,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!\NI'm so angry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバカの捨て身の執念のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ不覚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:47.25,default,,0,0,0,,Due to this idiot's desperation,\NI made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　名誉挽回のチャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,与えてやろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.29,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.19,default,,0,0,0,,Shall I give you a chance\Nto redeem your honour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:04.77,default,,0,0,0,,Once more...\NAnother round with 18mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 18ミリだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 生き死にの博打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.33,default,,0,0,0,,Another life or death gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　自らを奮い立たせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:15.70,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji brings himself up and bets\Nhis life on this final battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦に命を賭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった仲間のためにも命を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:19.74,default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of his\Ncomrades who have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:45.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回｢心血｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.98,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Heart's Blood.
